{"tid":453893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯收馬斐森回覆　不滿內容含糊　再致函要求確認是否查戴耀廷","createTime":"2017-10-31T15:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T17:38:57.000Z","uid":88681,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"0c258eb60e7c82f3b59336bd0c6f2007dea249de","tid":453893,"uid":88681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯多次去信香港大學校長及校委會主席等人，要求校方調查法律系副教授戴耀廷有否行為失當。何君堯晚上在facebook發帖，表示已收到港大校長馬斐森回信，但認為對方言辭非常含糊，事件「未解決」，已再去函要求對方清晰回答是否正式處理投訴。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯本月18日去信港大校委會主席李國章，要求校方澄清是否已正式接受他投訴戴耀廷行為失當。他晚上公開馬斐森信件，信中表示校委會主席收到來郵後，把信件轉交到他手上；而校方已知悉事件，會根據既定程序處理。何君堯認為馬斐森回覆言辭含糊，已再致函要求對方直接回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171031/s00001/7c25e7fe088d0fef52438a27da6b251a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171031%2Fs00001%2F7c25e7fe088d0fef52438a27da6b251a.jpg&h=a15bf3da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171031/s00001/7c29f130e112642f02280b1bbd767bee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171031%2Fs00001%2F7c29f130e112642f02280b1bbd767bee.jpg&h=a89e416c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171031/s00001/1509460116155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171031%2Fs00001%2F1509460116155&d=183tMSu8fj4vslgrYfXG%2BWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b087a989\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171031%2Fs00001%2F1509460116155&h=074debf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171031/s00001/1509460116155</a>"},{"pid":"50fd13330d2b3315600a57e9a1c337bf6329802b","tid":453893,"uid":88681,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10